OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FIt's a busy week at Hall Green
OL,7,     FHealth Centre as the doctors see
OL,8,     Flots of patients who are
OL,9,     Fstruggling to manage their weight.
OL,10,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,11,     FWith the computer system down, the
OL,12,     Fstaff resort to a whiteboard to
OL,13,     Fkeep track of everyone. Patients
OL,14,     Finclude two elderly men with
OL,15,     Fbreathing difficulties.
OL,16,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,17,     FDoctors treat a non-verbal young
OL,18,     Fman in a life-threatening
OL,19,     Fneurological emergency, while a
OL,20,     Fmidwife with severe spinal pain is
OL,21,     Ffeared to have cauda equina
OL,22,     Fsyndrome after back surgery.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
