OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA builder falls from a great
OL,7,     Fheight while working in a derelict
OL,8,     Ffarm building; a car wash employee
OL,9,     Fis stabbed dangerously close to
OL,10,     Ftheir liver.
OL,11,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,12,     FA look at misbehaving lumps, from
OL,13,     Fthe biggest (13cm) to the smallest
OL,14,     Fthat the dermatologists have ever
OL,15,     Ftreated.
OL,16,G0000 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,17,     FIn Coventry, a prolific shoplifter
OL,18,     Fis caught, and claims he steals
OL,19,     Fout of necessity. At a QD store
OL,20,     Fsomeone thinks they can get away
OL,21,     Fwith not paying for their
OL,22,     FChristmas shopping. (Ep2)
